title: Average US Snowfall by City
name: Average US Snowfall by City
description:
This dataset displays the average snowfall for 260 points around the United States. This data was collected through Swivel.com at: http://www.swivel.com/data_sets/show/1011367
Through: http://ols.nndc.noaa.gov/plolstore/plsql/olstore.prodspecific?prodnum=C00095-PUB-A0001
Snowfall (Including Ice Pellets and Sleet) - Average Total in Inches. Data through 2006. Beginning in April 1988 HAIL is also included under Snowfall. Therefore, some stations may show snowfall during the warm months.
This data was accessed on January 15, 2007
